&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot; align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://sachaai.com/images/homosexuality_std_risk.jpg&quot;&gt;Objection: Homosexuality brings more risks for STDs (Sexually Transmitted Diseases)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
