&lt;p class=&quot;_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM&quot;&gt;So what is wrong if a transgender woman cannot become pregnant? This does not kill her wish to become a mother.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;_1qeIAgB0cPwnLhDF9XSiJM&quot;&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;mozTocH2&quot; name=&quot;mozTocId378147&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Objection 10: The shape of reproductive organs is a witness that homosexuality is unnatural&lt;/h2&gt;
