		<title>The Suffering of Intersex Individuals Due to Illogical and Unjust Islamic Teachings</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://sachaai.com/index.php/en/lgbtq/the-suffering-of-intersex-individuals-due-to-illogical-and-unjust-islamic-teachings"/>
